datastring.dstemplatestring:
Case Description: This Clinical Trial report from Spain was received on 14-DEC-2020 regarding a 49-year-old

male patient (040-0003) who was enrolled in study protocol ALN-CC5-005 entitled, "A Phase 2 Study of

Cemadisiran in Adult Patients with IgA Nephropathy".

The patients medical history included IgA nephropathy, hypertension, diabetes mellitus Il and obesity.
(Continued on Additional Information Page)
